# Project Rules

- This project is the website for https://sideprojectsaturday.com
- Side project saturday is a casual, weekly social gathering where we meet at the val.town office from 9am til 12pm in downtown Brooklyn, NY to work on side projects.

## Technical constraints

- Use PNPM to manage dependencies
- Hono.js is the backend. Use hono client components if you need to write frontend code. 
- The environment is cloudflare workers
- If you add a new script to the package.json, also add a mise task to `mise.toml`
- Emails in the `src/emails` directory use `react-email`. It's the only place in this codebase that uses react. 